Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,----------ED01「Twinkle Starlight」----------
Comment: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:55.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,見上げた空高く
Comment: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:58.42,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,降り注ぐきらめきよ
Comment: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Twinkle，Brilliant，
Comment: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:03.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Wonder Starlight.
Comment: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:10.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,このまま　そっと目蓋とじても
Comment: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:19.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,胸にきらり　輝くよ
Comment: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:24.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,たとえばそうこんな雨の日
Comment: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:28.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,雲間から覗く空に
Comment: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:34.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,明日ヘの願いを込めて
Comment: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:39.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,きっとそこにあるよ（Eternal Starlight）
Comment: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:43.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,導くひかりを（Beyond The Night）
Comment: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:46.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,追いかけ続ける（Over The Blue Sky）
Comment: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:53.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,幼い日のような澄んだ瞳で
Comment: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:54.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,だから
Comment: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:58.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,無窮にまたたく星よ
Comment: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:01.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,希望の祈りたちよ
Comment: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:08.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,想いのせ　銀河の果てまでも
Comment: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:12.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Twinkle，Twinkle，Twinkle，Twinkle Star.
Comment: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:16.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Shiny，Bright In The Sky.
Comment: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Oh...
Comment: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:24.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Wonderful Twinkle Starlight.
Comment: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:55.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,抬头仰望无垠夜空
Comment: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:58.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,无数星辰悄然洒落
Comment: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,闪烁之间
Comment: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:03.37,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,漫天璀璨
Comment: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:10.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,即使轻轻地闭上双眼
Comment: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:19.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,无尽的光辉犹在心间
Comment: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:24.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,即使整天下雨淅淅沥沥
Comment: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:28.23,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,也想透过云隙仰望天际
Comment: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:34.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,然后许下明日的恳祈
Comment: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:39.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,它一定就在那{\fnFOT-Chiaro Std B}里{\fn}（永恒星光）
Comment: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:43.13,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,那指引我的绚丽（划过黑夜）
Comment: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:46.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,我会不住地寻觅（踏上碧空）
Comment: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:53.61,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,因为眼瞳依旧像儿时那般清晰
Comment: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:54.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以啊
Comment: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:58.33,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,无数闪烁的星辰啊
Comment: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:01.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,无数希望的祈愿啊
Comment: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:08.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,带着我的思念　飞向银河的尽头吧
Comment: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:12.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,闪烁明亮的星辰啊
Comment: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:16.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,放射光明在天际啊
Comment: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.49,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,哇~
Comment: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:24.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,闪烁星光洒满天
